19 SECTION 2. SECTION 13-37-501, MCA, IS AMENDED TO READ:
20 "13-37-501. Definitions. As used in this part, the following definitions apply:
21 (1) "Entity" means a partnership, association, limited liability company, joint venture, corporation,
22 or any other legal or commercial organization, or a combination of entities.
23 (2) "Foreign national" means:
24 (a) a government of a foreign country;
25 (b) a political party of a foreign country;
26 (c) an entity located outside of the United States unless that entity:
27 (i) is organized under or created under federal law, state law, or the law of another place subject
28 to the jurisdiction of the United States; and
