19 SECTION 3. SECTION 13-37-502, MCA, IS AMENDED TO READ:
20 "13-37-502. Prohibition on foreign national interference in election. (1) It is unlawful for a foreign
21 national, directly or through an intermediary, to make a disbursement for an electioneering communication, a
22 contribution, or an expenditure, or to make an express or implied promise to make a contribution or an
23 expenditure, in connection with any candidate election.
24 (2) It is unlawful for a person to:
25 (a) solicit, accept, or receive a contribution, expenditure, or disbursement described in subsection
26 (1) from a foreign national; or
27 (b) make a contribution, expenditure, or independent expenditure using any funds the person
28 knows were received from a foreign national for any purpose described in this section.
